The article is a presidential memorandum issued by Donald J. Trump on June 21, 2017. The memorandum delegates authority to the Secretary of Defense under the Consolidated Appropriations Act, 2017. It authorizes the Secretary of Defense to carry out the functions and authorities vested in the President by section 10005 of the Act. The memorandum also states that the delegation applies to any provision of any future public law that is the same or substantially the same as section 10005 of the Act. Finally, the memorandum directs the Secretary of Defense to publish the memorandum in the Federal Register.